<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;But if a pasture is run as a commons open to all, the right of each to use it <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:orange;">is not matched</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> by an operation responsibility to take care of it.&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
