Except <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>I haven't argued this</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.  Every one of my replies has been within the scope of the original argument, which had to do with the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>World Food Bank</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.  &quot;We have no obligation to the world's needy&quot; is in reference to the argument, which is about a <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>World Food Bank</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.  It is a misunderstanding on <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>your</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> part. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#4D4D4D><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/bthetribunaldotorg.showUserPublicProfile?gid=caledhontelrana>Caledhon TelRana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I read boards more<br>than I play EQ....</span><br>  Posts: 1566<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(9/17/03 9:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=876.topic&index=40>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: We have no obligation to the world's needy.</span><hr size=1> To begin with, I'd like to point out that this:<br>
<br>
&quot;Desperate people are easily influenced two-bit dictators and religious fanatics. Influenced to do things like strap bombs to their chests and fly planes into buildings.&quot;<br>
<br>
Is a load of BS.<br>
<br>
Terrorists are not poor or hungry.  Poverty does not result in terrorism.  If you doubt this, you have only to do a smidgen of research.<br>
<br>
Hayzen, yes, we agree that the World Food Bank is a bad idea, and I read your article, but from reading your responses, it has sounded to me like you yourself have gone beyond that single issue occasionally:<br>
<br>
&quot;Just giving people these things does not solve the problem, it does not help the problem, and it does not give people incentive to get themselves out of the rut&quot;<br>
<br>
Well, most of the times, yes... but not all the time.  There are cases when a shipload of food might actually be all that a nation requires to get it through a hard spot, the danger comes in assuming that a shipload of food will always be a good thing when delivered someplace where starving people reside.  It seems to me you have been arguing that a shipload of food is never a good thing when delivered to starving people, because it sets up a bad precedent (we'll always bail you out) even in cases where it might otherwise be a good idea.<br>
<br>
Anyway, if you were ONLY talking about the World Food Bank, then ignore that and a lot of what else I've said, since I guess you don't want to expand the argument at all.  That's not what it sounded like to me *shrug* <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showMessageRange?topicID=876.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showMessageRange?topicID=876.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showMessageRange?topicID=876.topic&start=61&stop=62>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showPrevMessage?topicID=876.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showNextMessage?topicID=876.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=876.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.emailToFriend?topicID=876.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.threadControl?topicID=876.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=876.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</